@startuml Sequence_Payment_Processing

actor Customer
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB
participant "Razorpay" as Payment
actor Admin

== Bill Creation ==

Admin -> Frontend: View Order
Frontend -> API: GET /api/orders/:id
API -> DB: Fetch order
DB --> API: Order details
API --> Frontend: Order data

Admin -> Frontend: Create Bill
Frontend -> API: POST /api/orders/:id/create-bill
API -> DB: Check if bill exists
DB --> API: No existing bill

API -> DB: Create Bill\n(amount = order.totalAmount,\nstatus = "Pending")
DB --> API: Bill created

API -> DB: Update order status\n(status = "Order Placed")
DB --> API: Order updated

API --> Frontend: Bill created
Frontend --> Admin: Bill details

== Customer Makes Payment ==

Customer -> Frontend: View Bills
Frontend -> API: GET /api/bills
API -> DB: Fetch customer bills
DB --> API: Bills list
API --> Frontend: Bills data
Frontend --> Customer: Display bills

Customer -> Frontend: Pay Bill
Frontend -> API: POST /api/payments/create\n(billId, amount)
API -> DB: Fetch bill details
DB --> API: Bill data

API -> Payment: Create payment order
Payment --> API: Payment order ID

API -> DB: Update bill\n(paymentMethod = "Razorpay")
DB --> API: Bill updated

API --> Frontend: Payment link
Frontend --> Customer: Redirect to payment page

== Payment Gateway Processing ==

Customer -> Payment: Enter payment details
Payment -> Payment: Validate payment
Payment -> Payment: Process payment

alt Payment Success
  Payment --> API: Payment webhook (success)
  API -> DB: Update bill\n(amountPaid = amount,\nstatus = "Paid",\npaidAt = now)
  DB --> API: Bill updated
  
  API -> DB: Add payment record
  DB --> API: Payment saved
  
  API -> DB: Update order status
  DB --> API: Order updated
  
  API -> DB: Create notification
  DB --> API: Notification created
  
  API --> Frontend: Payment success
  Frontend --> Customer: Payment confirmation
  
else Payment Failed
  Payment --> API: Payment webhook (failed)
  API -> DB: Update bill\n(status = "Pending")
  DB --> API: Bill updated
  
  API --> Frontend: Payment failed
  Frontend --> Customer: Error message
end

== Payment History ==

Customer -> Frontend: View Payment History
Frontend -> API: GET /api/bills/:id/payments
API -> DB: Fetch payment records
DB --> API: Payments list
API --> Frontend: Payment history
Frontend --> Customer: Display payments

note right of DB
  Bill Status Flow:
  Pending → Paid
  Payment Methods: Razorpay, Cash, Card, UPI
end note

@enduml


